Classes in gui.common used by gui.batches
Controller
          Controller is a base class that provides common functionality required by all controllers in the program (i.e., all controller classes extend Controller).
DialogBox
          Used to display modal dialog boxes.
DialogView
          Base class for all views that are displayed in dialog boxes.
IController
          IController defines functionality that is supported by all controllers in the program.
IView
          IView defines functionality that is supported by all views in the program.
View
          View is a base class that provides common functionality required by all views in the program (i.e., view classes extend View instead of JPanel).
